commit.message:
arm-protos.h: Reindent FL_FOR_* macro definitions.

2016-07-07  Thomas Preud'homme  <thomas.preudhomme@arm.com>

    gcc/
    * config/arm/arm-protos.h: Reindent FL_FOR_* macro definitions.

From-SVN: r238082
